            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-4-1649169519996-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has reduced, add the <strong>chopped hake</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 3-4 min further or until the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>chipotle spiced hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
